tissueExpression.summary: Spermatogonia in seminiferus ducts of testis exhibited strong cytoplasmic positivity. Glomeruli in kidney, goblet cells in small intestine and skeletal muscle displayed moderate positivity. Remaining normal tissues were negative.

Spermatogonia in seminiferus ducts of testis exhibited strong cytoplasmic positivity. Glomeruli in kidney, goblet cells in small intestine and skeletal muscle displayed moderate positivity. Remaining normal tissues were negative.
Few cases of melanomas along with a single case of squamous cell carcinoma of head&neck showed moderate to strong cytoplasmic immunoreactivity. Remaining cancer tissues were negative.
